  "format": "Sean benches Amanda to review the seventh live-action Transformers on his own, then runs through new streaming titles and takes a listener mailbag with producer Bobby Wagner: the Barbie-Oppenheimer double-feature order, the Mets as a disaster movie, and a pre-1960 Rewatchables wish list.",
  "segments": [
