        },
        {
          "title": "The Civil Dead",
          "year": 2023,
          "note": "Clay Tatum's indie with Whitmer Thomas as a ghost only his friend can see; Sean pitches it as Ghost Dad for two bros."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "discussion",
      "heading": "The correct order for Barbie and Oppenheimer",
      "note": "Julian and 53 others",
      "films": [
